  "title": "Relationship Manager/MNC Bank/ Salary Up to $4.5K",
  "description": "<p><strong>We are seeking individuals with a dynamic personality to be a part of a MNC. Selected candidates will be trained to build and nurture strong relationship with customers.</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Benefits:</strong></p>\n<p>Attractive remuneration compensation<br>\nFast-track career progression<br>\nTransportation allowance<br>\nTravel opportunity</p>\n<p><strong>Job Requirements:<br>\n </strong>Creative problem solving &amp; top notch organizational skills with attention to detail<br>\nPrioritize tasks according to urgency and meet tight deadlines with quality work, excellent time keeping<br>\nIn depth understanding of requirements involved in the lifestyle management of affluent, high-net worth individuals<br>\nExperienced in dealing with confidential information using discretion and sensitivity Excellent interpersonal skills - Outstanding telephone manner<br>\nIndependent, Confident with working under pressure<br>\nKnowledge of the Customer Service<br>\nMature and Polished appearance<br>\nGood team player and Reliable<br>\nFast learner and Self-starter</p>\n<p><strong>Qualification:<br>\n </strong>A recognized Degree/ Diploma in any field<br>\nFresher’s are welcome to apply!!!</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>EA Name: Louise Chia Chau Lu<br>\nRegistration No. R1769464<br>\nEA License No. 22C1201</p>\n<p><br></p>",
